summary: RaceMenu presets of the main characters from the visual novel The Arcana: A Mystic Romance
descriptionHtml:
Put together for some friends over on Tumblr. Eventually planning to make these into a follower mod but until then I may as well share the presets I'm using.

(I'm not terribly great at making male faces, so please bear with me on that!)

You will need:
[url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/68311/]KS Hairdos - Renewal[/url]
[url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/30823]Hale - Iridum Eyes[/url]
[url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/30411]Brows[/url]

Recommended Mods:
[url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/72586]Pride of Valhalla[/url]
[url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/82948]Vitruvia - Skin Texture Overhaul for Males[/url]
[url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/75915]KS Hairdos - Renewal Breast Weight Painted Hair[/url] (If you have HDT bazonkers)
[url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/1874]Bandit Eyepatch[/url]

Asra is Breton based
Nadia is Redguard based
Julian is Imperial based
However, I've included sculpt files if you don't want to stick with my headcanons.

Please don't make followers from my presets, I'm already planning on doing that myself!
Please don't use my presets as bases and post them online, personal use is fine.
Please contact me if you wish to upload these elsewhere.

This is definitely a work in progress, so any [b]constructive[/b] criticism would be much appreciated!
author: Eris
